How to get an image URL

  1. Right-click an image on the web and copy the images URL.
  2. Return to the search box and paste in the URL (Ctrl+V or Command+V).

Tip: Try dragging an image into the search box from your desktop or the web.

Learn about search by image
How to upload an image

  • Use the button below to open an image thats on your computer.

Google will automatically upload and search using the image.

Tip: Try dragging an image into the search box from your desktop or the web.
